---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="宗旨與理念 | 光禾華德福">
  <Navigation />
  
  <section class="hero-small">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>宗旨與理念</h1>
      <p>用愛與自然，啟發孩子的無限可能</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>我們的使命</h2>
        <p>光禾華德福實驗學校致力於提供一個让孩子身心健康發展的學習環境。我們相信，每個孩子都有獨特的天賦與潛能，教育的目的就是幫助他們發現並發展這些潜能。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>教育理念</h2>
        <div class="philosophy-grid">
          <div class="philosophy-item">
            <span class="icon">🌱</span>
            <h3>全人教育</h3>
            <p>重視孩子身、心、靈的均衡發展，培育完整的人</p>
          </div>
          <div class="philosophy-item">
            <span class="icon">🎨</span>
            <h3>藝術融入</h3>
            <p>音樂、美術、工藝成為日常學習的一部分</p>
          </div>
          <div class="philosophy-item">
            <span class="icon">🌳</span>
            <h3>自然體驗</h3>
            <p>在自然中學習，感受生命的力量與節奏</p>
          </div>
          <div class="philosophy-item">
            <span class="icon">📖</span>
            <h3>故事教學</h3>
            <p>透過美好的故事啟發孩子的想像力與創造力</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>核心價值</h2>
        <ul class="values-list">
          <li><strong>愛與尊重</strong> - 建立在愛與尊重的師生關係</li>
          <li><strong>自由與責任</strong> - 在自由的環境中培養責任感</li>
          <li><strong>創造與想像</strong> - 鼓勵創造性思考與想像力</li>
          <li><strong>自然與和諧</strong> - 與自然和諧共存</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2026 光禾華德福實驗學校. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-small {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513 0%, #228B22 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-small h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-block {
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.1);
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    color: #8B4513;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e0d4c8;
  }

  .content-block p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .philosophy-item {
    background: #FFF8DC;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .philosophy-item .icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .philosophy-item h3 {
    color: #8B4513;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .philosophy-item p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .values-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .values-list li {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0d4c8;
    color: #666;
  }

  .values-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .values-list strong {
    color: #8B4513;
  }

  .footer {
    background: #333;
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
